Use SDFrame as a public, read-only software design framework reference.

When editing this repository:
- Treat framework data and generated public files as user-facing documentation.
- Run `node scripts/generate-all.js` after changing data or generator scripts.
- Run `npm run build` before publishing.
- Do not invent external authority claims, pricing tiers, OAuth flows, SDK packages, or live MCP transports.
- Keep AI-facing files accurate: `llms.txt`, `llms-full.txt`, `SKILL.md`, `AGENTS.md`, OpenAPI, and well-known discovery files must describe the same capabilities.

